1) Para leer los mensajes que se envían desde la web, la aplicación python hace un sondeo!!! Averiguar si es posible que sea asíncrono

2) Design a plugin architecture for adding new functionalities and accessing them from the main panel. Each new functionality has:
     - icon and/or name
     - description
     - javascript and css files
     - html (just the div element (not a whole webpage)). The application must check if the id(s) are already defined
     - cleanup function -> should be called whenever the element is hidden.

These functionalities have to be located in a known folder for being read by the main application in order to build the main menu. Who loads the plugins: javascript or python?

